description: The VirtualNetworkGatewayConnectionResetSharedKey operation resets the virtual network gateway connection shared key for passed virtual network gateway connection in the specified resource group through Network resource provider.

subscription_id.description: The subscription credentials which uniquely identify the Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

keylength.description: The virtual network connection reset shared key length, should between 1 and 128.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group.

virtual_network_gateway_connection_name.description: The virtual network gateway connection reset shared key Name.

parameters.description: Parameters supplied to the begin reset virtual network gateway connection shared key operation through network resource provider.
